casebody.data:
Charles Lee DAVIS
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 30P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Charles Davis, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Ronald L. Moore, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 12th day of January 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Buncombe County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2005."
